, uidStr); err != nil {\n          return nil, err\n      }\n      if err := tx.
Commit(); err != nil {\n          return nil, err\n      }\n\n      // 3. 推送（
允许失败，仅记日志）\n      ...\n  }\n  ```\n- **依据**: `docs/architecture/laye
rs.md` 第 12.1 节"何时开启事务"明确说明"多表更新需要事务"；`docs/design-docs/tra
nsactions.md` 要求事务在 Biz 层开启。\n\n---\n\n## 严重问题（Major）\n\n### 3. S
